  "text": "In the present study, we evaluated the effects of PGE 2 on [Ca 2ϩ ] i responses in individual T cells using the Ca 2ϩ imaging technique. These assessments allowed us to ascertain variability in the [Ca 2ϩ ] i responses within the T cell population. We examined also the effects of PGE 2 on release of Ca 2ϩ from intracellular stores and its influx through the plasma membrane. Additionally, we ascertained the effect of intracellular cAMP, the second messenger generated in the action of PGE 2 , in the modulation of T cell [Ca 2ϩ ] i [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
